title: From which coaching institute did the NEET 2018 AIR 2 Rohan Purohit study? - Quora

response.answer_text: I have been noticing that there's a lot of confusion as to which institute did I study from since Aakash, Allen and Sri Chaitanya have claimed that I am a student of their institute. ( I know only of these 3 institutes which have claimed my name and I am unaware if any other institute had done so ) So let me clear things out. I gave ANTHE ( Aakash National Talent Hunt Exam) in 2015 and got 148 rank. So according to the Aakash policy, all the books would be free. As it was free I took it ( there's no disadvantage in taking the books ) I took Allen DLP and joined the classroom programme of Sri Chaitanya. So technically I am a student of these 3 institutes. But I took teaching from Sri Chaitanya and took help of Aakash and Allen books. Some people are telling that I have sold my ranks to these institutes after the ranks came out which is completely false. Thank you.
